---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — ACLEDS"
  description="About the African Centre for Learning Analytics and Educational Data Science"
>
  <section class="page-hero section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
      <h1>About ACLEDS</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">
        A research centre dedicated to generating rigorous, contextually valid
        knowledge about learning and education in Africa — using the tools of
        data science.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-main">
          <p class="eyebrow">Our Foundation</p>
          <h2>Why ACLEDS Exists</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p>
            Much of the educational research informing policy and practice in
            African schools originates outside the continent — imported
            wholesale without sufficient attention to local context, culture,
            infrastructure, or the specific challenges that characterise African
            educational systems.
          </p>
          <p>
            ACLEDS was established to address this gap directly. We produce
            scholarship that begins with African classrooms, African learners,
            and African educational realities — and that uses the analytical
            power of learning analytics and educational data science to surface
            insights that would otherwise remain hidden.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our work spans the generation of new knowledge, the development of
            methodological approaches suited to our context, and the translation
            of findings into recommendations that can actually reach teachers,
            curriculum designers, and policymakers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-aside">
          <div class="card card-dark">
            <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--gold)">Our Mission</p>
            <p
              style="color:rgba(232,237,244,0.8); margin-top:0.75rem; font-size:1.05rem; font-style:italic; line-height:1.7"
            >
              "To advance evidence-based education in Africa through rigorous,
              contextually grounded research in learning analytics and
              educational data science."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top:1.25rem">
            <p class="eyebrow">Our Approach</p>
            <ul class="approach-list">
              <li>Longitudinal research designs</li>
              <li>Mixed methods integration</li>
              <li>Transparent data practices</li>
              <li>Policy-focused dissemination</li>
              <li>School and community partnerships</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-fog">
    <div class="container">
      <div
        class="section-header"
        style="text-align:center; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto 3.5rem"
      >
        <p class="eyebrow">What Guides Us</p>
        <h2>Core Commitments</h2>
        <div class="divider" style="margin:1rem auto"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commit-icon">
            <svg
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              ><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"></path><path
                d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h4>Rigour</h4>
          <p>Methodological integrity in every study we conduct.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commit-icon">
            <svg
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              ><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"></path><circle
                cx="9"
                cy="7"
                r="4"></circle><path
                d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h4>Inclusion</h4>
          <p>
            Centring learners and communities most often excluded from research.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commit-icon">
            <svg
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              ><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h4>Integrity</h4>
          <p>
            Transparent reporting and ethical data stewardship at all times.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commit-icon">
            <svg
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              ><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h4>Impact</h4>
          <p>Research designed to reach policy, not just publication.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container cta-inline">
      <div>
        <h2>Work With Us</h2>
        <p>
          We are open to collaborations with researchers, institutions, schools,
          and policy partners.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; flex-shrink:0">
        <a href="/team" class="btn btn-dark">Meet the Team</a>
        <a href="/collaborate" class="btn btn-primary">Collaborate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 5rem;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .page-hero-sub {
    color: rgba(232, 237, 244, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 58ch;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-main p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .about-main h2 {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .approach-list {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .approach-list li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .approach-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .commitment-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    background: var(--true-white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74, 96, 128, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .commit-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .commitment-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .commitment-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .cta-inline {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--fog);
  }
  .cta-inline h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .cta-inline p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
